programme.title: America's Test Kitchen: The Next Generation
programme.desc: Today in the Test Kitchen, the final four cooks have four hours to put together a cohesive, three-course meal. The catch: they must include one affordable cut of meat. programme.title: America's Test Kitchen: The Next Generation
